PrimedGun is a Dolphin ReduX/Dolphin-derived project focused on Metroid Prime
VR support. It is not the upstream Dolphin Emulator project.

Most of the original Dolphin-derived source code in this repository is licensed
under the GNU General Public License version 2 or later. PrimedGun changes and
new source files are distributed under the same GPL-2.0-or-later terms unless a
file states a different compatible license through its SPDX header.

Some source files and bundled third-party components are derived from other
projects and may carry different GPL-compatible license terms. Per-file license
information is provided through SPDX tags where available. The license texts
referenced by those tags are kept in the LICENSES/ directory.

PrimedGun does not include or license any commercial game data. Users must
provide their own legally obtained game file and saves.

This repository preserves Dolphin/Dolphin ReduX attribution and licensing
requirements because PrimedGun remains a derivative work.

SPDX information: https://spdx.dev/
